    "As the degree of hydroxylation increases, the depletion region becomes narrower.",
    "This indicates stronger interfacial structuring and enhanced surface-liquid contact on more hydrophilic surfaces.",
    "In particular, the fully hydroxylated surface shows the most pronounced layering near the interface.",
